name: Abhishek Enterprises
overview:
Established in the year 1998, we, “Abhishek Enterprises”, we are able to manufacture and supply a wide variety of Li Ion Battery Pack, Power Bank With LCD, CC-CV Charger & DC-DC Converter, LED Light & Li Polymer Battery . Our vendors are constantly involved in supplying us with premium quality raw material for the manufacture of these products. Hence our entire product range exhibits high tenacity, robust construction, exceptional power back up and handling convenience.

Our Products: Li Polymer Battery Power Bank CC-CV Charger & DC-DC Converter LED Light

Our Team: Our organization is immensely supported by a huge team of trained and qualified professionals who are are highly skilled to satisfy any needs or requirements of our respected clients. These professionals are highly efficient in their respective fields and they strive hard to achieve distinctive requirements of our valued clients.

Infrastructure: We have a state-of-the-art infrastructure in the company to facilitate better and efficient business dealings. This facility is equipped with advanced tools and cutting edge technology, which enables us to manufacture a quality range of products.

Our Quality: We have always believed that quality is the utmost criteria for any product hence we follow the same thing while manufacturing our wide product range. We have a team of quality controllers whose main job is to ensure that all our products checked thoroughly in accordance to the global principles.
